{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_10_01",
  "title": "成宮すず 1話 思い入れのある曲",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月ストがBIG4になってしばらくした頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Some time after Moon Tempest became BIG4",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "地方でのフェスに出演して、すぐに戻って\n新曲のMV撮影……分かっていてもやはり忙しないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Performing at a countryside festival and filming a new song's MV\nright after returning… I knew it‚ but it's really hectic.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "タクシーが来るまで少しでも休んでおこう\n体調はどうだ？　何かあったらすぐに言ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's rest as much as we can until the taxi comes.\nHow are you feeling? Tell me right away if anything happens.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.53333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "この程度なんともありませんわ\n自ら望んだスケジュールですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is nothing.\nIt's a schedule I wanted myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.1999999483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になってからはずっとこんな日々が\n続いていますもの。すっかり慣れましたわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ever since becoming BIG4‚ it’s been like this\nall the time. I'm completely used to it now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.9999999483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "それに……フェスから帰る前に麻奈様のお墓参りも\nさせていただけましたから。感謝していますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides… I was also able to visit Mana-sama's grave\nbefore returning from the festival. I'm grateful for that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.4999999483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈様に現況を報告して……\n初心に返ることが出来ましたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I reported the current situation to Mana-sama…\nand I was able to return to my original intentions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "念願のBIG4になったとはいえ\n微塵も油断することなく邁進してまいりますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though we've become the long-awaited BIG4‚\nI’ll keep moving forward and never let my guard down!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.4999999483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そう言ってもらえると\n時間を作った甲斐があったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It makes me happy to hear you say that.\nIt was worth making the time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "ところで{user}さん\n来月には月ストの単独ライブがありますわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ {user}-san‚\nthere's a Moon Tempest solo live coming up next month‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.4932137984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.5999999483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "その時のセンターをどうするかについて\nお話……と言うよりは、決意表明がありますの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About the center position for that…\nI'd like to say… No‚ I have a declaration of resolve.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "決意表明？　どういうことだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A declaration of resolve? What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.1999999483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.1999999483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃は……どりきゅんとの戦いで、月ストのセンター\nとしての力をはっきりと見せてくれましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono… showed her power as the center of Moon Tempest\nin the battle with Dorikyun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.5333332817
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "さらには昨日のフェス。雨の影響で私達四人が遅れる中\n一人でステージに立って堂々と歌う姿は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's more‚ at yesterday's festival‚ while the four of us were delayed due to the rain‚\nI saw her figure standing alone on stage and singing with dignity…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.5333332817
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "言うのも悔しいですが、神々しささえ感じましたわ\nSNSでも、とても話題になっていましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's frustrating to say‚ but I even felt a sense of divinity.\nIt was a hot topic on SNS too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "そんな訳で、最近ファンの間でも「月ストのセンターは\nやっぱり琴乃」という声が高まっていますの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why‚ more and more fans have been saying‚\n\"Moon Tempest's center is obviously Kotono.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.7333332817
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……琴乃の評判が上がるのはいいことだが\nセンターを巡って競ってるすずとしては、悔しいよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… It's good that Kotono's reputation is rising‚ but\nit must be frustrating for you‚ Suzu‚ who is competing for the center position.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.166666615
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですのよ！　そろそろ、私がセンターに立って\nどーんと存在感を示したいですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right! It's about time I stood in the center\nI want to show my presence with a bang!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "それに……今度のライブは、月ストがBIG4になって\n初めての単独ライブでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides… the next live will be Moon Tempest's first solo live\nafter becoming BIG4‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.5999999483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "「すずの晴れ舞台はなんとしても見たい」と\n成宮家の親族が揃って観に来ますの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All of the Narumiya family relatives said \"We definitely want to see\nSuzu's glorious performance‚\" and they will come to see it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ご親族が揃って……！？\n凄いな、もはやすずの応援団じゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All of your relatives are coming…!?\nThat's amazing‚ they're basically your fan club.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.4333332817
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "ですから……単独ライブでは\nなんとしてもセンターに立ちたいのです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So… at the solo live‚\nI definitely want to stand in the center.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.8333332817
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "すずの気持ちは分かった\n簡単に結論を出すことは出来ないが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand your feelings‚ Suzu.\nI can't come to a conclusion easily‚ though…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "誰がセンターを務めるのか、どうセンターを決めるのか\n琴乃や他のメンバーも含めて、話し合いの場を作るよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll arrange a meeting with Kotono and the other members\nto discuss who should be the center‚ and how to decide.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.4333302299
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
